race.description: Advanced Electrical & Data 5th Grade Ht 6 H
race.comment: WILGUNYA KNIGHT (2) goes very well this trip starting 11 times for five wins and three minors. Recorded a 4.5 lengths win (16.57) in a Grade 5 last time at Casino. Expected to be in the finish. SEND A TEXT (1) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a slick early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten 8 lengths at this track over 350m in 20.93. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. BUGATTI QUEEN (4) was prominent early off a low draw but weakened and dropped out when 5th over 350m at this track in Grade 5 company. Has ability and is one of the better chances. NALU (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.
